{"tid":1958242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［TVB日任4/4］打破同溫層！鄉土U汪要人！","createTime":"2020-04-04T13:08:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:50:52.000Z","uid":75759,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"190dc83f23e5e40d0c1da80ae70e4e02bdd65d94","tid":1958242,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sazPqik.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsazPqik.jpg&h=c2dcf098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【🎈週末特別任務】請將______(㊙️)公司嘅醜聞傳遍藍絲🗣<br />\n 4 April 2020<br />\n<br />\n⚔️【行動概要】<br />\n應承咗唔喺TVB落廣告，但卻反口落返廣告嘅公司，大家有興趣可以睇返佢點呃人: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/posts/551238112399709/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fposts%2F551238112399709%2F&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDDwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=30978083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/posts/551238112399709/</a><br />\n而相信藍絲既死穴就係錢🤑 一齊真實嘅公司營運問題傳編俾對家，將佢哋都拉埋入抵制大軍，咁佢仲唔早日執笠？🤪☺️<br />\n<br />\n⚔️【行動詳情】<br />\n<br />\nStep 1️⃣ 去Discuss, Uwants推post<br />\n👉🏻 Discuss<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28973119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D28973119&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDDwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=25bb8c13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=28973119</a><br />\n👉🏻 Uwants<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=20126460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D20126460&d=635WHVioB6XLrmiJ2plDDwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=3f0aac4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=20126460</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️注意事項：<br />\n🔹俾少少心機回覆，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果只係回覆&quot;推&quot;、表情灌水，嚴重者可能被封鎖帳戶</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔹留言應該係&quot;真實&quot; 嘅評價<br />\n🔹Template：&quot;真係好恐怖&quot;, &quot;反正大把選擇，咁唔安全都係用第二間&quot;<br />\n🔹隔幾日再回覆，推足一星期<br />\n<br />\nStep 2️⃣ Whatsapp<br />\n將醜聞spread去Whatsapp藍絲group。<br />\n<br />\nStep 3️⃣ 進階 - 開post：<br />\n喺唔同討論區相關分台自行開post，但如果見到手足已開post，推post就得（請注意相關版規）"},{"pid":"7155904dbb30336c113086e28dc1dfc76c63d449","tid":1958242,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:08:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3e0224263801a00f656be317bcbf29203e255a0","tid":1958242,"uid":288537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:09:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b2d57082b7b6848b6ea8733933100b1aaf91498","tid":1958242,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ba8ef9880374ba7a73e48f504df20fc1273de5f2","tid":1958242,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:09:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86771388f18fc09e6c81b19cca49348c51a495ea","tid":1958242,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deff2e903f209ef917979b7e73316752b19b62dc","tid":1958242,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b066a2d663465f39acbbed19df6a56d32e370d","tid":1958242,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:10:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"92f7d77c77f541bbb2dc28c0b309c97a2b2805e5","tid":1958242,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:10:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7e134ca772171c1b7acb6608f490f6538d5b3e48","tid":1958242,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score